User "1" -- "0..*" Enterprise : possède
Enterprise "1" -- "0..*" Domaine : contient
Plan "1" -- "0..*" Abonnement : attribue
User "1" -- "0..*" Abonnement : souscrit
Paiement "1" -- "1" Abonnement : valide
User "1" -- "0..*" Paiement : effectue
Plan "1" -- "0..*" Paiement : concerne

Conversation "1" -- "0..*" Message : contient
User "1" -- "0..*" Message : envoie
User "1" -- "0..*" Conversation : participe
Service "1" -- "0..*" Conversation : concerne
Message "0..1" -- "0..*" Message : reply_to

Enterprise "1" -- "0..*" Service : propose
Domaine "1" -- "0..*" Service : catégorise
User "1" -- "0..*" Service : crée

Service "1" -- "0..*" RendezVous : reçoit
User "1" -- "0..*" RendezVous : client
Enterprise "1" -- "0..*" RendezVous : gère

RendezVous "1" -- "0..1" Review : reçoit
User "1" -- "0..*" Review : rédige
User "1" -- "0..*" Review : prestataire

Message "1" -- "0..*" AiFeedback : feedback
User "1" -- "0..*" QrLoginToken : génère
User "1" -- "0..*" LoginHistory : historique

@enduml
